    cout << "\n\n\t\t\t======= ðŸ…¢ðŸ…£ðŸ…¡ðŸ…¤ðŸ…š ðŸ…ŸðŸ…ðŸ…¡ðŸ…šðŸ…˜ðŸ…¡ =======\n";
    cout << "\t\t\t Lokasi Parkir: " << spot.location << "\n";
    cout << "\t\t\t Barcode: " << generateBarcode(12) << "\n";
    cout << "\t\t\t=======================================\n\n";
}

